## Visual Studio / C# standard gitignore

# Build outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Pp]ackages/

# Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.docstates
*.dbmdl
*.aps
*.opendb
*.sdf
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Mono / VS Mac
.mono/
*.m4n
*.m4a

# ReSharper / JetBrains
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

# Office temporary files (Word/Excel)
~$*
